dp-desktop-app â€” Release Artifacts and Verification
==================================================

This repository publishes the dp-desktop-app as an executable Java application
via GitHub Releases.

Each release corresponds to a Git tag of the form:

  rel-<version>

Example:
  rel-1.12.0-rc8

------------------------------------------------------------
Release Contents
------------------------------------------------------------

Each release contains:

  dp-desktop-app-<version>.jar
    Executable desktop application JAR.

  dp-desktop-app-<version>.jar.sha256
    SHA-256 checksum for integrity verification.

------------------------------------------------------------
Download and Installation
------------------------------------------------------------

1. Download the JAR and checksum from the GitHub Release page.

2. Verify the checksum:

   sha256sum -c dp-desktop-app-<version>.jar.sha256

   The output should indicate:
     dp-desktop-app-<version>.jar: OK

3. Run the application:

   java -jar dp-desktop-app-<version>.jar

------------------------------------------------------------
Configuration
------------------------------------------------------------

The application is typically configured via external YAML files supplied by the
data-platform installer.

------------------------------------------------------------
Notes
------------------------------------------------------------

- dp-desktop-app communicates with dp-service at runtime.
- It is normally distributed as part of the Data Platform installer.
